metadata.name: The only one
metadata.description:
There are celestial objects in the world that are special and incomparable, such as the stars, the moon, other planets. And no matter how much we look for something similar, they are all individual and that value is incommensurable. We are like that ourselves, we all have that uniqueness in us.

Original painting. Oil on canvas. 
18 x 24 cm 
Year: 2021

NFT: 2000 x 2688 pixels  
Solovyova Anastasia
